  "detailed_description": "October 16th, 1987<br>Black Ridge Mountains<br><br>Private investigator Matthew Barker is on his way to meet up with his partner Daniel Houghton. A recent string of disappearances possibly linked to a serial killer in the town of Black Ridge has left the sheriff's department stretched thin.<br><br>Matthew and Daniel have been tasked by the sheriff's department to investigate a manor located in the outskirts of Black Ridge. The MacCarthy family, owners of the manor are thought to have disappeared and left the manor abandoned over a year ago. Locals have reported strange sightings and sounds from the areas surrounding the manor.<br><br>Once the investigation is complete they are to report any findings to The Black Ridge Sheriffs Department.<br><br>Exsanguinate is a puzzle-intensive giant escape room-style survival horror game.  Solve fun but challenging puzzles while being stalked by a clever AI.<br><br>Explore the mansion.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1850240/extras/112ee4cfa9af61a0aed68a8f11f193e1.poster.avif?t=1769168874\" width=598 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1850240/extras/112ee4cfa9af61a0aed68a8f11f193e1.webm?t=1769168874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1850240/extras/112ee4cfa9af61a0aed68a8f11f193e1.mp4?t=1769168874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Find the clues.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1850240/extras/124b9970085278c7f3b8aba186df7dbf.poster.avif?t=1769168874\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1850240/extras/124b9970085278c7f3b8aba186df7dbf.webm?t=1769168874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1850240/extras/124b9970085278c7f3b8aba186df7dbf.mp4?t=1769168874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Solve the puzzles.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1850240/extras/0ba6ba48b5e718b74af70a2e63962041.poster.avif?t=1769168874\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1850240/extras/0ba6ba48b5e718b74af70a2e63962041.webm?t=1769168874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1850240/extras/0ba6ba48b5e718b74af70a2e63962041.mp4?t=1769168874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Survive the night.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1850240/extras/9b2b3eccb95ad069d6e2b1376a388562.poster.avif?t=1769168874\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1850240/extras/9b2b3eccb95ad069d6e2b1376a388562.webm?t=1769168874\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1850240/extras/9b2b3eccb95ad069d6e2b1376a388562.mp4?t=1769168874\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
